messages.message: Hey @mfichman -- I wanted to ask if this was still something we could look at. Cass does have a workaround in place, but this has been an open issue for a bit
Yes, let me take a look today, & create a ticket!
@Armaan -- that trace timed out. Do you know the best way for me to find another one?
